metadata.title: Skechers Max Cushioning Arch Fit - Swift Moves
description: Women's Skechers, Max Cushioning Arch Fit - Swift Moves Sneaker. Enhanced with dual-cushioning technologies, the Skechers Max Cushioning Arch Fit Swift Moves slip-on sneaker is the ultimate in casual comfort. This athletic shoe features a soft mesh fabric upper with removable Arch Fit insole and a lightweight ULTRAGO cushioned midsole for superior shock absorption and lasting support.. Soft mesh fabric with smooth synthetic overlays with high apex front and padded collar Removable Ortholite foam technology insole layer provides long-term cushioning Arch Fit design with anatomically designed support Lightweight and responsive ULTRA GO cushioning NRT - Natural Rocker Technology for a smooth heel to toe transition Goodyear Rubber performance outsole
